The Kitchen - Season 2, Episode 12




The Corn Show

The hosts are serving up delicious summer corn three new ways. Shop and Store your summer fruits and vegetables for peak flavor. Marcela, our Master of Mexican fires up tasty tamales. We'll show you how to Trick Out your Cookout. Chopped judge and chef extraordinaire Marc Murphy treats our gang to a fresh seafood salad with scallops. And when It's 5:00 Somewhere our mix master, Geoffrey makes a GZ Cocktail as the hosts share their latest Drinkstagrams.




Original Air Date: 05-Jul-2014
